#set($pagetitle='About')
<p class="heading">About Rule maintenance Application</p>
<p>Version: ${version} (${lastupdate})</p>
<p>This web-application uses modern, state-of-the-art technologies to present the content to the user. on the other hand the application can be rapidly updated and maintained. this is achieved by using a MVC (Model-View-Controller) paradigm and by implementing an advanced template engine (Velocity).</p>
<p>Given these advantages, paired with a high-speed quality database, RAD (Rapid Application Development) is indeed possible.</p>
<p>The applied technologies of the application are:</p>
<ul>
	<li>Tomcat Web Server. Most used web-server worldwide. Dynamic reloading of code.</li>
	<li>Java Servlets. The strength, performance and security of Java used for controlling the application and the business objects.</li>
	<li>Beanshell scripts for on-the-fly code maintenance</li>
	<li>Velocity Template Engine. Gives flexibility in design, splits development from web-design and is very fast.</li>
	<li>MySql Database. Most used open-source database worldwide. Relational, transactional, fast and modern. Easy to deploy, manage and maintain.</li>
</ul>
<br>
<p>Requirements for this application:</p>
<ul>
	<li>HTML 4 conformal browser.</li>
	<li>Some functionality requires Javascript.</li>
</ul>
